    "endTime": 835.6,
    "text": "part rushed two angels out to sodom to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 835.6,
    "endTime": 837.6,
    "text": "warn lot to gather up his folks and get"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 837.6,
    "endTime": 839.44,
    "text": "out of dodge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 839.44,
    "endTime": 842.639,
    "text": "lot hurt the angels warning but delayed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 842.639,
    "endTime": 844.48,
    "text": "they didn't have all day to wait so they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 844.48,
    "endTime": 846.959,
    "text": "grabbed lot's hands and his two"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 846.959,
    "endTime": 849.12,
    "text": "daughters hands and his wife's hands and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 849.12,
    "endTime": 851.6,
    "text": "hurried them out of sodom and angel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 851.6,
    "endTime": 852.639,
    "text": "shout"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 852.639,
    "endTime": 854.24,
    "text": "escape to the mountain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 854.24,
    "endTime": 856.639,
    "text": "whatever you do don't look back just as"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 856.639,
    "endTime": 859.12,
    "text": "god starts raining down fire on sodom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 859.12,
    "endTime": 860.8,
    "text": "and gomorrah i can't figure out how"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 860.8,
    "endTime": 863.44,
    "text": "gamora got dragged into this but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 863.44,
    "endTime": 865.76,
    "text": "lot and his folks are running"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 865.76,
    "endTime": 868.079,
    "text": "fleeing all that destruction kicking up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 868.079,
    "endTime": 870.72,
    "text": "dust while the lord rains down death and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 870.72,
    "endTime": 871.6,
    "text": "then"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 871.6,
    "endTime": 873.279,
    "text": "for some reason"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 873.279,
    "endTime": 875.279,
    "text": "lot's wife looks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 875.279,
    "endTime": 876.88,
    "text": "back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 876.88,
    "endTime": 880.56,
    "text": "god turns her into a pillar of salt"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 880.56,
    "endTime": 881.839,
    "text": "remember"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 881.839,
    "endTime": 883.279,
    "text": "lot's wife"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 883.279,
    "endTime": 885.76,
    "text": "jesus says"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 885.76,
    "endTime": 888.48,
    "text": "but i've got a question"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 888.48,
    "endTime": 891.44,
    "text": "why did she look back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 891.44,
    "endTime": 892.959,
    "text": "did she look back because she didn't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 892.959,
    "endTime": 895.199,
    "text": "want to miss the mayhem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 895.199,
    "endTime": 897.279,
    "text": "wanted one last glimpse of a city on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 897.279,
    "endTime": 899.04,
    "text": "fire"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 899.04,
    "endTime": 900.56,
    "text": "did she look back because she wanted to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 900.56,
    "endTime": 902.56,
    "text": "be sure that her people were far enough"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 902.56,
    "endTime": 904.959,
    "text": "from danger to breathe a little easy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 904.959,
    "endTime": 907.04,
    "text": "i'm so nosy and selfish sometimes those"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 907.04,
    "endTime": 909.12,
    "text": "likely would have been my reasons if i'd"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 909.12,
    "endTime": 911.12,
    "text": "been in her shoes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 911.12,
    "endTime": 914.16,
    "text": "but what if something else was going on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 914.16,
    "endTime": 915.839,
    "text": "with this woman"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 915.839,
    "endTime": 918.0,
    "text": "lot's wife"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 918.0,
    "endTime": 921.12,
    "text": "what if she could not bear the thought"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 921.12,
    "endTime": 923.6,
    "text": "of leaving those people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 923.6,
    "endTime": 926.72,
    "text": "all alone to burn alive even for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 926.72,
    "endTime": 928.8,
    "text": "righteousness sake"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 928.8,
    "endTime": 931.279,
    "text": "isn't that possible"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 931.279,
    "endTime": 932.959,
    "text": "if it is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 932.959,
    "endTime": 935.36,
    "text": "then this backward glance of a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 935.36,
    "endTime": 937.12,
    "text": "disobedient woman may not be a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 937.12,
    "endTime": 939.44,
    "text": "cautionary tale after all it may be the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 939.44,
    "endTime": 942.24,
    "text": "bravest act in all the bible"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 942.24,
    "endTime": 944.0,
    "text": "even braver than the act that holds the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 944.0,
    "endTime": 946.959,
    "text": "whole book together crucifixion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 946.959,
    "endTime": 948.16,
    "text": "we are told"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 948.16,
    "endTime": 949.839,
    "text": "that up on calvary"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 949.839,
    "endTime": 952.16,
    "text": "on an old rugged cross"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 952.16,
    "endTime": 954.079,
    "text": "jesus gave his life to save everybody"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 954.079,
    "endTime": 955.92,
    "text": "billions and billions of strangers for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 955.92,
    "endTime": 957.68,
    "text": "all time to come"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 957.68,
    "endTime": 959.68,
    "text": "it's a nice thing to do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 959.68,
    "endTime": 963.12,
    "text": "made him famous that's for sure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 963.279,
    "endTime": 966.0,
    "text": "but lot's wife was killed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 966.0,
    "endTime": 968.639,
    "text": "turned into a pillar of salt"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 968.639,
    "endTime": 971.68,
    "text": "all because she could not turn her back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 971.68,
    "endTime": 973.36,
    "text": "on her friends"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 973.36,
    "endTime": 976.32,
    "text": "the wicked men of sodom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 976.32,
    "endTime": 978.959,
    "text": "and nobody even wrote the woman's name"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 978.959,
    "endTime": 980.8,
    "text": "down"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 980.8,
    "endTime": 982.959,
    "text": "oh to have the courage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 982.959,
    "endTime": 984.959,
    "text": "of lot's wife"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 984.959,
    "endTime": 986.8,
    "text": "that's the kind of courage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 986.8,
    "endTime": 988.56,
    "text": "we need today"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 988.56,
    "endTime": 992.0,
    "text": "the courage to put ourselves over there"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 992.0,
    "endTime": 993.759,
    "text": "the courage that says that either all of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 993.759,
    "endTime": 996.32,
    "text": "us have to be or none of us can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 996.32,
    "endTime": 999.68,
    "text": "be for any of us to be free"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 999.68,
    "endTime": 1001.68,
    "text": "the courage to stand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1001.68,
    "endTime": 1004.32,
    "text": "with other vagabonds in the street with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1004.32,
    "endTime": 1006.56,
    "text": "all the wretched of the earth"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1006.56,
    "endTime": 1009.36,
    "text": "to form an army of the least of these"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1009.36,
    "endTime": 1010.639,
    "text": "with the faith"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1010.639,
    "endTime": 1013.759,
    "text": "that from the naked crust of all we are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1013.759,
    "endTime": 1015.199,
    "text": "we can build"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1015.199,
    "endTime": 1016.88,
    "text": "a better world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1016.88,
    "endTime": 1018.13,
    "text": "thank you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1018.13,
    "endTime": 1021.08,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1021.08,
    "endTime": 1024.889,
    "text": "[Music]"
  }
]